url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%88%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%8E%D9%91%D8%AB%D9%8E"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to inherit","examples":[{"text":"وَلَقَدْ كَتَبْنَا فِي ٱلزَّبُورِ مِنْ بَعْدِ ٱلذِّكْرِ أَنَّ ٱلْأَرْضَ يَرِثُهَا عِبَادِيَ ٱلصّٰلِحُونَ","english":"And already have We written in the Book [of David's psalms], after [mentioning in] the Exposition [of Mosaic Law] (the Torah), that the land shall be inherited by My righteous servants."},{"text":"الصِّدِّيقُونَ يَرِثُونَ ٱلْأَرْضَ وَيَسْكُنُونَهَا إِلَىٰ ٱلْأَبَدِ.","english":"The righteous shall inherit the land, and dwell therein for ever."}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"cause someone to inherit, to transfer by will, to bequeath","tags":["ditransitive"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of وَرِثَ (wariṯa) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Cognate with Hebrew יָרַשׁ (yāráš)."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n41827","headword_ar":"وَرِثَ","root":"wrv","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yarivu","text_ar":"يَرِثُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) an instance of deviation from a constant rule, there being only the following verbs of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faEila","text_ar":"فَعِلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"which have the aorists of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yafoEilu","text_ar":"يَفْعِلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"only, namely,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waviqa","text_ar":"وَثِقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wariva","text_ar":"وَرِثَ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wariEa","text_ar":"وَرِعَ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"warima","text_ar":"وَرِمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wariYa","text_ar":"وَرِىَ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wafiqa","text_ar":"وَفِقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waliYa","text_ar":"وَلِىَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wamiqa","text_ar":"وَمِقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Ibn-Málik and others,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waSiba","text_ar":"وَصِبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA, art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waSb","text_ar":"وَصب"},{"kind":"text","text":":) the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"w","text_ar":"و"},{"kind":"text","text":"falls out in"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yarivu","text_ar":"يَرِثُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[&c.] because it occurs between"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Y","text_ar":"ى"},{"kind":"text","text":"and kesreh; and in those persons of the aor. which begin with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A","text_ar":"ا"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"t","text_ar":"ت"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"n","text_ar":"ن"},{"kind":"text","text":"because these letters are changed from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Y","text_ar":"ى"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is the original: (S:) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wirovN","text_ar":"وِرْثٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_irovN","text_ar":"اـِرْثٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) in which the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"w","text_ar":"و"},{"kind":"text","text":"is changed into"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^","text_ar":"ا"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rivapN","text_ar":"رِثَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) in which the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a substitute for the [elided]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"w","text_ar":"و"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wiraAvapN","text_ar":"وِرَاثَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K,) [the most common form] and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_iraAvapN","text_ar":"اـِرَاثَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) and accord. to some"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"miyraAvN","text_ar":"مِيرَاثٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", but this is an error, for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mifoEaAlN","text_ar":"مِفْعَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is not one of the measure of inf. ns., (ISd,) [but it is used by some of the professors of practical law as an inf. n.,] and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"turAvN","text_ar":"تُراثٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Msb [but see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wirovN","text_ar":"وِرْثٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"below]:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He inherited."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, &c.) You say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wariva A^abaAhu","text_ar":"وَرِثَ اَبَاهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He inherited"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the property of"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his father:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K:) but the original phrase is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wariva maAla A^abiyhi","text_ar":"وَرِثَ مَالَ اَبِيهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He inherited the property of his father."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) Also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wariva mino A^abiyhi","text_ar":"وَرِثَ مِنْ اَبِيهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eanohu","text_ar":"عَنْهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", A,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He inherited of his father:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he inherited part of the property of his father."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wariva Al$~aYo'a mino A^abiyhi","text_ar":"وَرِثَ الشَّىْءَ مِنْ اَبِيهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He inherited the thing of,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from, his father."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) When you say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wariva zayodN A^abaAhu maAlFA","text_ar":"وَرِثَ زَيْدٌ اَبَاهُ مَالًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Zeyd inherited of his father property"},{"kind":"text","text":"], the word"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mAlA","text_ar":"مالا"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a second objective complement, if the verb be doubly trans.; or it is a substitute of implication ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"badalu A@$otimaAlK","text_ar":"بَدَلُ ا@شْتِمَالٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":") for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zyd","text_ar":"زيد"},{"kind":"text","text":". (MF.) You say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"warivotuhu","text_ar":"وَرِثْتُهُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maAlahu","text_ar":"مَالَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"majodahu","text_ar":"مَجْدَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I inherited his property,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and, (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his glory:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"warivotuhu Eanohu","text_ar":"وَرِثْتُهُ عَنْهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I inherited it from him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K","TA","ISd"]},{"entry_id":"n41831","headword_ar":"وَرْثٌ","root":"wrv","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  What is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fresh, juicy,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"moist,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of things. (K.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n41832","headword_ar":"وِرْثٌ","root":"wrv","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_irovN","text_ar":"اـِرْثٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[see 1] and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"turaAvN","text_ar":"تُرَاثٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(in which the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"t","text_ar":"ت"},{"kind":"text","text":"is originally"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"w","text_ar":"و"},{"kind":"text","text":", S,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"miyraAvN","text_ar":"مِيرَاثٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(originally"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"miworaAvN","text_ar":"مِوْرَاثٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"w","text_ar":"و"},{"kind":"text","text":"being changed to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Y","text_ar":"ى"},{"kind":"text","text":"because of the kesreh immediately preceding it, S.)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"What is inherited; an inheritance,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a heritage:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or, accord. to some,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wrv","text_ar":"ورث"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"myrAv","text_ar":"ميراث"},{"kind":"text","text":"are used with reference to property, or wealth; and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Arv","text_ar":"ارث"},{"kind":"text","text":"with reference to rank or quality, nobility or eminence, reputation, or the like, in Arabic,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hasab","text_ar":"حَسَب"},{"kind":"text","text":": (M:) [the pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"myrAv","text_ar":"ميراث"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mawaAriyvu","text_ar":"مَوَارِيثُ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] [See also art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^riv","text_ar":"ارِث"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^uvobutuwAEalaY ma$aAEirikumo h`*ihi faA_in~akumo EalaY","text_ar":"اُثْبُتُواعَلَى مَشَاعِرِكُمْ هٰذِهِ فَاـِنَّكُمْ عَلَى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_irovK mino A_irovi A_ibor`hiyma","text_ar":"اـِرْثٍ مِنْ اـِرْثِ اـِبْرٰهِيمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Remain ye steadfast in the observance of these your rites,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ceremonies; for ye act"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"therein"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"according to usage inherited from Abraham."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA, [app. from A'Obeyd].) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_irovN","text_ar":"اـِرْثٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in art"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^rv","text_ar":"ارث"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lahumo A_irovu majodK","text_ar":"لَهُمْ اـِرْثُ مَجْدٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They have an inheritance of glory."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["M"]}]}}